      "text": "Green Lake (Chisago City, Minnesota)\nGreen Lake is a lake in Chisago City, Minnesota, United States. This lake is sometimes also referred to as \"Big Green Lake\" because it is connected to Little Green Lake by a channel. Green Lake was named from the fact its waters are green from the high algae content.",
